OL,7,FOne of the UK's longest, most beautiful
OL,8,Fand best loved rivers is "dying" as
OL,9,Fheavy pollution kills its wildlife, say
OL,10,Fexperts who warn that the plight of the
OL,11,FWye is a worrying sign for the rest of
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,FThe river runs 155 miles from its
OL,15,Fsource in the Cambrian Mountains in mid
OL,16,FWales to the Severn Estuary in the
OL,17,FBristol Channel, and has been voted the
OL,18,Fnation's favourite.
OL,3,CWhy the impending 'death' of one of the
OL,4,CUK's longest and best loved rivers
OL,5,Cshould worry us all
